<h1>Friendly Parrots</h1>

<h2>About Parrot</h2>

<p>Parrot are popular and intelligent pet that come in different sizes and species. Some parrot can live upto <strong>100 years</strong> but requires a lot of attention and special care.<br><br> Parrot can be trained to fly freely in the house and never fly away.
   With proper care and attention,parrot can be great pets and long-time companions.
</p>

<h2>Types of Parrot</h2>
